sequenceDiagram
    participant Customer
    participant MobileApp
    participant BackendAPI
    participant SupabaseDB

    Customer->>MobileApp: Add to cart
    MobileApp->>MobileApp: Update cart state
    
    Customer->>MobileApp: Proceed to checkout
    MobileApp->>MobileApp: Navigate to checkout screen
    
    Customer->>MobileApp: Confirm order
    MobileApp->>BackendAPI: Create order
    BackendAPI->>SupabaseDB: Insert order
    SupabaseDB-->>BackendAPI: Order created
    BackendAPI-->>MobileApp: Order confirmed
    MobileApp-->>Customer: Show success message